searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"TorkGovernance","doc":"On-device AI governance with PII detection, redaction, and cryptographic receipts.","ref":"TorkGovernance.html"},{"type":"module","title":"Usage - TorkGovernance","doc":"result = TorkGovernance.govern(\"My SSN is 123-45-6789\")\n    result.action   #=> :redact\n    result.output   #=> \"My SSN is [SSN_REDACTED]\"\n    result.receipt   #=> %{receipt_id: \"...\", input_hash: \"...\", ...}","ref":"TorkGovernance.html#module-usage"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.govern/2","doc":"Apply governance rules to the input text.\n\nDetects PII, applies redaction if found, and generates a cryptographic receipt.","ref":"TorkGovernance.html#govern/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Options - TorkGovernance.govern/2","doc":"* `:action` - Override the default action (`:redact`)","ref":"TorkGovernance.html#govern/2-options"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - TorkGovernance.govern/2","doc":"iex> result = TorkGovernance.govern(\"Hello world\")\n    iex> result.action\n    :allow\n\n    iex> result = TorkGovernance.govern(\"SSN: 123-45-6789\")\n    iex> result.action\n    :redact","ref":"TorkGovernance.html#govern/2-examples"},{"type":"module","title":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix","doc":"Phoenix-specific governance helpers.\n\nProvides functions to govern controller params and response data.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.html"},{"type":"module","title":"Usage in a Controller - TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix","doc":"defmodule MyAppWeb.ChatController do\n      use MyAppWeb, :controller\n      alias TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix, as: TorkPhoenix\n\n      def create(conn, params) do\n        governed = TorkPhoenix.govern_params(params)\n        # Use governed params...\n        json(conn, %{status: \"ok\"})\n      end\n    end","ref":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.html#module-usage-in-a-controller"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.govern_params/2","doc":"Govern a params map by detecting and redacting PII in string values.\n\nRecursively traverses the map and governs all string values.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.html#govern_params/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.govern_params/2","doc":"iex> TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.govern_params(%{\"name\" => \"SSN: 123-45-6789\"})\n    %{\"name\" => \"SSN: [SSN_REDACTED]\"}","ref":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.html#govern_params/2-examples"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.govern_response/2","doc":"Govern response data before sending as JSON.\n\nRecursively traverses the data structure and redacts PII in string values.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix.html#govern_response/2"},{"type":"module","title":"TorkGovernance.PII","doc":"PII detection and redaction using regex patterns.","ref":"TorkGovernance.PII.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.PII.detect/1","doc":"Detect all PII matches in the given text.\n\nReturns a list of `%{type: atom, match: string}` maps.","ref":"TorkGovernance.PII.html#detect/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - TorkGovernance.PII.detect/1","doc":"iex> TorkGovernance.PII.detect(\"SSN: 123-45-6789\")\n    [%{type: :ssn, match: \"123-45-6789\"}]","ref":"TorkGovernance.PII.html#detect/1-examples"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.PII.redact/1","doc":"Redact all PII in the given text, replacing matches with type-specific placeholders.","ref":"TorkGovernance.PII.html#redact/1"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - TorkGovernance.PII.redact/1","doc":"iex> TorkGovernance.PII.redact(\"SSN: 123-45-6789\")\n    \"SSN: [SSN_REDACTED]\"","ref":"TorkGovernance.PII.html#redact/1-examples"},{"type":"module","title":"TorkGovernance.Plug","doc":"Plug middleware for Tork governance.\n\nAutomatically governs incoming request bodies for PII and attaches\nthe governance receipt to `conn.assigns[:tork_receipt]`.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Plug.html"},{"type":"module","title":"Usage in a Phoenix Router - TorkGovernance.Plug","doc":"pipeline :governed do\n      plug TorkGovernance.Plug\n    end\n\n    scope \"/api\", MyAppWeb do\n      pipe_through [:api, :governed]\n      post \"/chat\", ChatController, :create\n    end","ref":"TorkGovernance.Plug.html#module-usage-in-a-phoenix-router"},{"type":"module","title":"TorkGovernance.Receipt","doc":"Cryptographic receipt generation for governance operations.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.html"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.build/4","doc":"Build a governance receipt for an operation.\n\nGenerates a unique receipt ID, SHA-256 hashes of input and output,\nand a UTC timestamp.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.html#build/4"},{"type":"function","title":"Examples - TorkGovernance.Receipt.build/4","doc":"iex> receipt = TorkGovernance.Receipt.build(\"input\", \"output\", [], :allow)\n    iex> is_binary(receipt.receipt_id)\n    true","ref":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.html#build/4-examples"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.generate_id/0","doc":"Generate a unique receipt ID.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.html#generate_id/0"},{"type":"function","title":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.hash/1","doc":"Compute a SHA-256 hash of the given text.","ref":"TorkGovernance.Receipt.html#hash/1"},{"type":"extras","title":"Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"# Tork Governance Elixir SDK\n\nOn-device AI governance with PII detection, redaction, and cryptographic receipts for Elixir and Phoenix applications.","ref":"readme.html"},{"type":"extras","title":"Installation - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"Add `tork_governance` to your list of dependencies in `mix.exs`:\n\n```elixir\ndef deps do\n  [\n    {:tork_governance, \"~> 0.1.0\"}\n  ]\nend\n```","ref":"readme.html#installation"},{"type":"extras","title":"Quick Start - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"```elixir\nresult = TorkGovernance.govern(\"My SSN is 123-45-6789\")\n\nresult.action        #=> :redact\nresult.output        #=> \"My SSN is [SSN_REDACTED]\"\nresult.pii_detected  #=> [%{type: :ssn, match: \"123-45-6789\"}]\nresult.receipt       #=> %{receipt_id: \"rcpt_...\", input_hash: \"sha256:...\", ...}\n```","ref":"readme.html#quick-start"},{"type":"extras","title":"PII Detection - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"```elixir\nmatches = TorkGovernance.PII.detect(\"Contact john@example.com or call 555-123-4567\")\n#=> [%{type: :email, match: \"john@example.com\"}, %{type: :phone, match: \"555-123-4567\"}]\n\nredacted = TorkGovernance.PII.redact(\"SSN: 123-45-6789\")\n#=> \"SSN: [SSN_REDACTED]\"\n```","ref":"readme.html#pii-detection"},{"type":"extras","title":"Supported PII Types - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"| Type | Example | Redaction |\n|------|---------|-----------|\n| SSN | 123-45-6789 | [SSN_REDACTED] |\n| Email | john@example.com | [EMAIL_REDACTED] |\n| Phone | 555-123-4567 | [PHONE_REDACTED] |\n| Credit Card | 4111-1111-1111-1111 | [CREDIT_CARD_REDACTED] |\n| IP Address | 192.168.1.1 | [IP_REDACTED] |","ref":"readme.html#supported-pii-types"},{"type":"extras","title":"Phoenix Integration - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"","ref":"readme.html#phoenix-integration"},{"type":"extras","title":"Plug Pipeline - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"Add the governance plug to your router pipeline:\n\n```elixir\npipeline :governed do\n  plug TorkGovernance.Plug\nend\n\nscope \"/api\", MyAppWeb do\n  pipe_through [:api, :governed]\n  post \"/chat\", ChatController, :create\nend\n```\n\nAccess the governance result in your controller:\n\n```elixir\ndefmodule MyAppWeb.ChatController do\n  use MyAppWeb, :controller\n\n  def create(conn, params) do\n    receipt = conn.assigns[:tork_receipt]\n    governed_text = conn.assigns[:tork_result].output\n\n    json(conn, %{\n      message: governed_text,\n      receipt_id: receipt.receipt_id\n    })\n  end\nend\n```","ref":"readme.html#plug-pipeline"},{"type":"extras","title":"Controller Helpers - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"Use the Phoenix adapter to govern params directly:\n\n```elixir\ndefmodule MyAppWeb.UserController do\n  use MyAppWeb, :controller\n  alias TorkGovernance.Adapters.Phoenix, as: TorkPhoenix\n\n  def create(conn, params) do\n    governed_params = TorkPhoenix.govern_params(params)\n    # governed_params has all string values redacted for PII\n\n    json(conn, %{status: \"ok\"})\n  end\n\n  def show(conn, _params) do\n    user = get_user()\n    governed = TorkPhoenix.govern_response(user)\n    json(conn, governed)\n  end\nend\n```","ref":"readme.html#controller-helpers"},{"type":"extras","title":"Cryptographic Receipts - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"Every governance operation generates a verifiable receipt:\n\n```elixir\nresult = TorkGovernance.govern(\"Sensitive data\")\n\nresult.receipt.receipt_id   #=> \"rcpt_a1b2c3...\"\nresult.receipt.timestamp    #=> \"2026-02-08T12:00:00Z\"\nresult.receipt.input_hash   #=> \"sha256:9f86d08...\"\nresult.receipt.output_hash  #=> \"sha256:abc123...\"\nresult.receipt.pii_count    #=> 1\nresult.receipt.action       #=> :redact\n```","ref":"readme.html#cryptographic-receipts"},{"type":"extras","title":"License - Tork Governance Elixir SDK","doc":"MIT","ref":"readme.html#license"}],"proglang":"elixir","content_type":"text/markdown","producer":{"name":"ex_doc","version":"0.40.1"}}